## 🖥️ Wazuh Agent — Windows Deployment

### 1. Install Agent via PowerShell (Admin)

```powershell
msiexec /i "wazuh-agent-4.9.2-1.msi" WAZUH_MANAGER="192.168.248.132" /l*v "C:\wazuh-install.log"
```

### 2. Register Agent on Ubuntu Manager

```bash
sudo /var/ossec/bin/manage_agents
# Select A to add agent
# Name: WindowsHost
# IP: 192.168.248.1
# Select E to extract key
```

### 3. Apply Key and Start Service

In Wazuh Agent GUI on Windows:
- Paste the authentication key
- Set Manager IP: `192.168.248.132`
- Click Save

```powershell
NET START WazuhSvc
```

