## 🔍 File Integrity Monitoring (FIM)

### Configuration

Edit the agent configuration file on Windows:
```
C:\Program Files (x86)\ossec-agent\ossec.conf
```

Add inside the `<syscheck>` block:
```xml
<directories realtime="yes">C:\Users\Selld\Test</directories>
```

Restart the agent:
```powershell
NET STOP WazuhSvc; NET START WazuhSvc
```

### Testing FIM

```powershell
# Create test file
echo "test file" > C:\Users\Selld\Test\prueba.txt

# Modify test file
echo "modified" >> C:\Users\Selld\Test\prueba.txt

# Delete test file
Remove-Item C:\Users\Selld\Test\prueba.txt
```

